      • onCommandSend

        void onCommandSend(boolean success,
                 int commandType)
        Result of send instruction.
        参数:
        success - Whether send success
        commandType - Command type

      • onResponseEnterOTA

        void onResponseEnterOTA(boolean enter,
                      int failedReason)
        Device return the result of request enter OTA.
        参数:
        enter - Whether to enter the OTA. True for enter, false for not.
        failedReason - If enter==false, this parameter indicates the reason for the failure. 1.Low Battery Others. Unknown reason.

      • onResponseAlarmList

        void onResponseAlarmList(java.util.List<WristbandAlarm> alarms)
        Device return the result of request alarm list.
        参数:
        alarms - Alarm list.

      • onResponseNotificationConfig

        void onResponseNotificationConfig(NotificationConfig config)
        Device return the result of request notification config.
        参数:
        config - Notification config

      • onResponseWristbandVersion

        void onResponseWristbandVersion(WristbandVersion version)
        Device return the result of request wristband version.
        参数:
        version - Version info

      • onResponseWristbandConfig

        void onResponseWristbandConfig(WristbandConfig config)
        Device return the result of request wristband config.
        参数:
        config - Wristband all config.

      • onResponseBattery

        void onResponseBattery(int percentage,
                     int charging)
        Device return the result of request battery.
        参数:
        percentage - Battery percentage
        charging - Whether in charge. 1 for charge, 0 for not.

      • onFindPhone

        void onFindPhone()
        Wristband find phone.

      • onUserUnBind

        void onUserUnBind(boolean success)
        User unbind callback.If unbind success, the connection will close after this callback.
        参数:
        success - Whether unbind successful. True for success, False for failed.

      • onOpenHealthyRealTimeData

        void onOpenHealthyRealTimeData(int healthyType,
                             boolean success)
        Open healthy real time data result.
        参数:
        healthyType - IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_HEART_RATE IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_OXYGEN IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_BLOOD_PRESSURE IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_RESPIRATORY_RATE IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_ECG
        success - Open success.True for success, false for failed.

      • onCloseHealthyRealTimeData

        void onCloseHealthyRealTimeData(int healthyType)
        Close healthy real time data result.
        参数:
        healthyType - IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_HEART_RATE IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_OXYGEN IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_BLOOD_PRESSURE IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_RESPIRATORY_RATE IDevicePerformer.HEALTHY_TYPE_ECG

      • onResultHealthyRealTimeData

        void onResultHealthyRealTimeData(int heartRate,
                               int oxygen,
                               int diastolicPressure,
                               int systolicPressure,
                               int respiratoryRate)
        Health data returned by the wristband in real time. There is no ecg data in this callback. onResultEcgRealTimeData(byte[]) If the item is 0, ignore this data.
        参数:
        heartRate - Heart rate data
        oxygen - Oxygen data
        diastolicPressure - Diastolic pressure data,
        systolicPressure - Systolic pressure
        respiratoryRate - Respiratory rate

      • onResultEcgRealTimeData

        void onResultEcgRealTimeData(byte[] data)
        Ecg raw data returned by the wristband in real time. The two byte is a group representing ecg/heart rate data. Less than one set of data needs to be discarded.
        参数:
        data - raw datas

      • onOpenGSensor

        void onOpenGSensor(boolean success)
        Open GSensor real time data result.
        参数:
        success - Open success.True for success, false for failed.

      • onCloseGSensor

        void onCloseGSensor()
        Close GSensor real time data result.

      • onResultGSensor

        void onResultGSensor(byte[] data)
        GSensor raw data returned by the wristband in real time. The three byte is a group representing x/y/z sensor data. Less than one set of data needs to be discarded.
        参数:
        data - raw datas

      • onCameraTakePhoto

        void onCameraTakePhoto()
        Wristband request camera take photo.

      • onHungUpPhone

        void onHungUpPhone()
        Wristband request hung up phone.

      • onSyncDataStart

        void onSyncDataStart(int result)
        Sync data start.
        参数:
        result - Whether to start successfully. PerformerListener.SyncResult

      • onSyncDataEnd

        void onSyncDataEnd(boolean success)
        Sync data end.
        参数:
        success - Whether sync successfully. True for success ,false for failed.

      • onSyncDataResult

        void onSyncDataResult(java.util.List<SyncRawData> datas)
        All sync raw data. In the synchronization process, this method may be called 0 or more times. The data type in the list is same for one calls.

        Notice:The method that is not called by the main thread.

        参数:
        datas - Sync raw datas.List is not empty, and size > 0.

      • onSyncDataTodayTotalData

        void onSyncDataTodayTotalData(TodayTotalData data)
        Total data of the today.

        Notice:The method that is not called by the main thread.

        参数:
        data - TodayTotalData.

      • onSyncDataSleepTotalData

        void onSyncDataSleepTotalData(java.util.List<SleepTotalData> datas)
        If WristbandVersion.isSleepMonitorEnable() is true, the method will call back for result sleep history data which contains at most 7 datas.

        Notice:The method that is not called by the main thread.

        参数:
        datas - Sleep history data which contains at most 7 datas, may be null or empty.

      • onSyncDataEcgResult

        void onSyncDataEcgResult(java.util.List<EcgBean> ecgBeanList)
        If WristbandVersion.isEcgEnable() is true, the method will call back for result ecg data.

        Notice:The method that is not called by the main thread.

        参数:
        ecgBeanList - Ecg Datas.Not null and not empty.
